General.Name: Soup Restaurant Group Limited
General.Description: Soup Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates restaurants. It operates through Operation of Restaurants and Food Processing, Distribution and Procurement Services segments. The company sources, supplies, processes, and distributes raw materials and food products; and provides procurement, and job training and vocational rehabilitation services. It operates restaurant outlets in in Singapore and Malaysia under the Soup Restaurant, Soup Restaurant HERITAGE, TEAHOUSE, CAFE O, and POT LUCK brands, as well as one franchised outlets in Indonesia. The company was formerly known as Soup Restaurant Group Limited and changed its name to Soup Holdings Limited in May 2022. Soup Holdings Limited was incorporated in 1991 and is headquartered in Singapore.
